content.detailedDescription:
Witness by 2 individuals.

we had just returned from am interfacility transport on an ambulance. the davis monthan afb airshow was that weekend.  i was in the bathroom when my partner said, "hey, you are missing the thunderbirds leaving."  i came outside and saw about 10 brightly lit objects above the mountains approximately 12 miles to our ne.  several object came out from behind the low mountains and began ascending up to very high altitudes following the previous objects,  i estimate the altitude to be approximately 8000 feet agl.  as the object traveled east, they began to fade in intensity.  then, the last object i was visually following streaked what appeared to be straight south at an amazing speed and instantaneously.

teh objects all has a street light  (redish orange) color.  i dawned onme that no plane have any kind of avoidance lights of this color.  i was initially in the mindset of my partner's original assessment of the lights being the thunderbirds flying team"  it was near the end of the event that i became aware that there are not nearly that many thunderbird aircraft.
content.summary: 15 to 20 object seen coming out behind a mountain.

content.detailedDescription: Cerca july 1975 my brother and i entered the woods behind two of our childhood friends homes between by are lane westboro ma and what is now the ballpark.  brian pointed out a shape in the tree, it was facelike, and the tree then began moving rapidly with little ambient wind.  a few seconds later the wind picked up.  i told him we should run.  we ran to the edge of the marsh, he saw a footprint about twenty incheslong and odd looking.  it was oblong.  we proceeded toward a sand pit i yelled go left it is big and cannot follow through the more dense woods and thicket.  we got scratched up by the thorns and emerged at a pond out of a normal smelling marsh.  we assumed later fecal matter seeped from septic systems making the pond stinky.  the pond was in a clearing no felled trees or branches overhung it.  we were cutoff, needed to cross to exit fast.  i remember my legs and feet getting caught up in what felt like sticks, i pulled them upwards, they broke free easily, what felt like sticks lightly hitting my legs but not floating, they were not buoyant but not heavy. the pond got deeper, muck up to our knees, some particles scratched our legs. we exited the pond and sand pit, ran home. we went to the laundry room and almost threw up from the rancid smell, what smelled like rotting flesh and fecal matter.  we never spoke of it.  we're terrified.  movies came out with it in it with sagorny weaver and we were sickened.It looked like the attached photos but not these photos
content.summary: Encountered what looked like a very large green xenomorph

content.detailedDescription: While sitting on my sled waiting to go down hill at a popular location named salerno circle, i was suddenly held on both sides of my sled by my brother & a friend of his. they, wishing to play a cruel joke on me, turned my sled around and pushed me over the back side of the hill which was uncleared and very steep. the sled took off at a tremendous speed which made it nearly impossible to avoid the many trees & rocks that were in my path. as i approached the very bottom of the hill i unfortunately ran in to a tree. upon contact my body was thrown a short distance in to another tree which ruptured my kidney & spleen rendering me paralyzed from the waist down. as i lay there unable to move anything other than my head & arms, i constantly kept watch up the hill waiting for my brother to come down and help me; to my surprise he left me there. this caused me to go in to a panic, because where i was located was so deep in the woods no one could possibly see me, or even find me unless they were told i was there. after about 30 minutes of laying there it began to get dark; as the darkness set in i noticed a strange orange glow in the sky above the trees; then suddenly what appeared to be a heat force surrounded me; than a figure appeared before me that resembled an old faded brown robe. i could not understand what was happening, so in my attempt to figure it out i began to look for details so as to make sense of what i was experiencing; but what i could not see confused me even more. in my search to figure out what was before me i noticed there were no hands or feet to be seen; it was just a robe that covered some form of energy. than suddenly i was placed on my sled, and it began to move within this heat field out of the woods with this robe in the front of me creating the appearance that someone was pulling me along. as we moved out to the sidewalk along the main street i constantly looked through this heat field and watched cars going by, and wondered if they could see me as i could see them; even though the heat field made everything appear a bit blurry. in quick time i was pulled directly to the front door of our house; and upon my arrival the rope attached to the sled that was held by the robe dropped to the ground and the robe floated off and disappeared into the darkness.
content.summary: I was surrounded by a heat force which transported me out of a life threatening situation.

content.detailedDescription: Me, my sister and some friends were metal detecting in a nearby building site. my sister shouted "look at that shooting star" we all looked up and i said that's not a shooting star, i knew this because the tail ended but the object was still there, it split into two parts, one shot off but the other came towards us, as it got closer we shouted for our parents to come, they heard us and came running out thinking one of us was in trouble, by this time the object was clearly visible, hovering above a field you could see the object was spinning slowly with a dull humming sound, it started coming towards us and i can remember my mum holding us with shear terror at what we were witnessing, it moved to the left of us and went behind a wooded area and slowly went behind the woods as if was landing. less an a minute later it came back up form the woods and returned to the spot it was hovering before, it then moved slowly right and then shot off with massive speed
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Shooting star split into 2. one shot off the other came towards us

content.detailedDescription:
I was inside home spending sometime on the internet when i decided to strench my legs and scan the sky (yes i have this habit since kid). it was 2:30am (aprox)

but the sky had too many clouds, except for 2 breaches directly overhead. 
then i saw this blueish light, it was abnormally fast for an airplane, the color was also abnormal, it came from west to east, it was very bright but small like a dot, very much like jupiter or venus, except that it was very blueish. it went over the clouds, i could still see it badly and vanished probably because of the cloud. i thought, strange, suspicious, lets check some websites to see if it was an airplane or a satelite flare os something like that. no, no confirmation from any websites.

i went back outside, my dog started barking a lot, i looked back at sky and a few seconds latter i saw 2 or 3 more lights coming from diferent directions thru the breach on the cloudscover. i knew it wasnt airplane or helicopter, i came back inside and took the phone (fixed line) and called my wife at work (she is a nurse) and started telling her what i just saw but still looking up hunting for more and then i saw 2 more times as i was speaking with her. then the breach in the cloudcover closed and i spent about 30 minutes scaning but i saw nothing, the dog stopped barking and i went inside to chew what i just saw.

there is a small possibility to be a drone, but this make little sense at all. brasil is a poor country, not many people have money to buy those expensive toys. it is 2am why someone would fly an expensive drone at 2am, why someone would fly at night on a purelly residential/rural area with nothing interesting? why someone would fly at 2am over cloudcover? but still it could be a drone. or it could be an et object. 

one more thing. it is not my 1st time, actually i had other richier much more vivid experiences with ufos and etos and in 2 ocasions (this one being the 2nd) i feel that i had a psychic conection just before the event, this time i was hearing some music, was in facebook and then i had this suden spike to move my focus to think about ufos, but i didn't entered any website, i just got outside to strench the lag before start to look for new information on the subject.
content.summary: Blueish bright dot fling overhead from diferent directions

content.detailedDescription: I was driving from cass lake, mn heading south on hwy 371 on my way to the northern lights casino in walker, mn around 2:30am.About 10 miles out from walker i noticed a bright point of light in the se ahead of me. i thought it might be a bright star. as i drove the point of light begsn to grow continuously. at first i thought it to be a plane but it was moving to slowly towards me. it had no flashing lights so i know it wasn't a helicopter either nor was it a hot air balloon. i slowed my speed to about 5-10 mph as i watched it approach and grow in size. the object continued its path until it hovered over head. the object was shaped similar to an hourglass. both the bottom and top structures were round like hockey pucks. bottom was like 2 pucks stacked then the middle was hourglass shaped then 2 more hockey pucks atop that. on the top of the top strucure (hockey pucks for lack of better shape comparison) a very tall spire almost like a radio tower continued for about 100ft. the spire had blue/green, red and white lights continuously covering it. the puck sections each were the approximate size of 4 story buildings and both had a continuous clean, bright white light that wrapped around with round red,green and orangish lights spuraticly above and below white light all around the puck shaped portion. the middle curved section between the puck shaped portions was about 50-75ft high also with lights. the object at its closest to me was about 100-200ft above ground and above me moving about 1-5 mph. i reached for my spot light i use to shine deer but was unable to reach it with an intention of shining it at the object. the object continued past me and i accelerated and continued on to the casino. there are 3-4 towers with ligjts along this section of hwy between cass lake and walker. there is also a private landing strip along the hwy. this object was not one of the towers or anything that would use a landing strip or pad. objects this size and shape should not be in the sky or able to fly. when the object was ovet head i lowered my window and i could hear no sound from object. no engine or sound of burners as in a hot air balloon. it also appeared to have a metal exterior. no visable windows. the white light was like ive never seen. hard to explain. it was the cleanest, brightest white light i've ever seen. all the lights were. when i arrived at the casino i ran into a friend at the entrance. as i explained to him what i had just witnessed a door security guy overheard my conversation. he approached and he said he has seen the same shaped object before as well. m a biologist and have been very skeptical of these kind of stories, as they are a dime a dozen here in northern minnsota, especially on reservations. now i don't know what to do or think about it.
content.summary: Looked like bright star in distance. flew at me at very slow velocity until over head then hovered. hourglass shape about 8-10 storys high

content.detailedDescription:
On new years eve at approximately 12:30 am my family and i were celebrating the ending of 2016 and beginning of 2017. we were barbecuing and drinking outside on the front porch. my adult nephew asked out loud " hey, what are those lights up there?" "they're coming this way." i walked out on the sidewalk to see and i saw an amber light quietly, slowly, and steadily, passing over head and i asked my adult daughter to video it with her phone. it began to fade out and then disappeared. as i turned to the direction that it came from i saw 2 more lights coming in our direction. same color, size, path, and speed. i asked my daughter to video them also. she did but she did not have too much space on her phone so when those faded out approximately in the same place as the first one she stopped recording. that wasn't it because we saw 2 more appear about 2 blocks away, it was a cloudy night and the lights just appeared below the clouds and come straight down our street again, same routine. she began recording again, by this time we were all excited not to mention tipsy. we had quite a bit of fireworks going off in the neighborhood that night but not on our block. you can hear some in the video in the background. but what we saw was definitely not fireworks. then we saw the last 2 lights appear and begin coming down the same path, by this time we couldn't believe what we were seeing. they all came down our street with absolutely no sound. they were the same color and as soon as the first pair would disappear the next two would appear a couple of blocks away. we didn't feel frightened or anything like that, just in awe. by the time the last two were going over us we were waving at them and wishing them a happy new year.
on the 3rd of january i saw that another houstonian family celebrating the same night also saw and recorded video of what looks to me to be the same lights but their sighting was a little different as they saw more than 2 at a time. i also began searching youtube to see if i could find any other houston sightings and i happened upon a video that was shot on new years of 2013. they also looked like the same type of lights. so i'm not sure what is going on but i am sure that these lights were not planes or helicopters, drones or lanterns and definitely not fireworks.
content.summary: New years eve night, 4 witnesses saw amber lights flying 2  at a time following same path and disappear above our heads. i personally saw 7 lights total.

content.detailedDescription: Observed a green white object flying east to west while driving in the west coast highway towards hilary boat harbour. i was shocked to see it and excited, it flew out of sight possibly landing in the ocean, was moving extremely fast.
content.summary: Object flying east to west - sparks coming out of top as it flew

content.detailedDescription:
Filled out at mufon headquarters, with witness on the phone, by field investigator l. flechtner 16609, on january 24th, 2017
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
i was waiting, in my backyard,for my dad to take me to boy scouts. i was sitting on a swing when i noticed a large silver saucer craft hovering near crescent lake. i jumped off the swing and ran towards the lake in our back yard. the craft was about 50 feet round with a dome on it. the craft was silver, but the top part was very bright white. the craft seemed to wobble slightly, but to immediately correct itself.
it was tree tip high and came towards me and ended up hovering over our house. i ran inside to tell my dad and get him to come outside, but he didn't. when i came back outside it was still there. when i looked up inside of the bottom of the craft, i could see two bright white lights rotating in side. one went clockwise and the other went counterclockwise. 
then it slowly moved toward the lake and hovered over the edge of the far side of the lake. it then moved 4 or 5 blocks near the banyan trees and stoped. a laser like beam shot out of the craft and entered the water at an angle. that lasted for 2 seconds. then the craft slowly moved towards the south, then slowly arose to the sky until it looked like a star.

i was in boy scouts at the time, so i think it was about 1969. i lived near the lake until 1974 when we moved. i don't remember what month it was. it was late in the day, just as the sun was setting. the whole thing lasted about 15 minutes. not sure what color the laser light was, didn't know about lasers at the time.
content.flightPath: Stationary,Hovering then path,Straight-line path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: I was sitting on a swing when i noticed a large silver saucer craft hovering near crescent lake.

content.detailedDescription:
I was watching stars from my terrace (8th floor) which i usually do as exercise for eyes. i get a full view of sky from north to southwest from here. 
at around 10.15pm four faint(but clearly visible) greenish white starlike lights (orbs) appeared at north flying in west to east direction at very high speed. their shape was vertices of isosceles triangle with fourth light as midpoint of other two(like an arrowhead). they were visible for only 1 sec before vanishing or fading as they flew towards east(30 degree above horizon). their trajectory was curving just before disappearing as they suddenly started pointing towards northeast.
i was shocked and tried to calm down as i thought it may have been an airplane or a helicopter. but commercial airplane airplanes fly only north-south direction here and there was no sound. and moreover no airplane or heli can fly so fast. but i still thought it must have been my imagination.
i decided to continue observing and after 15-20 mins they appeared again, this time they flew from west to east in a straight path with a little lower speed than before. this time i was convinced and decided to report to mufon. i wasn't able to capture any photo regretfully as my phone camera not so good.
content.summary: 4 greenish white starlike lights flew across the sky at high speed

content.detailedDescription:
Traveling west on edmound rd,near saddlebrooke. noticed bright yellow/red glowing light from a vehicle at ~800 ft. moving s to n.Size of glow ~30-50ft.Got out of car to watch as it passed overhead.
it continued going n at approx 50 mph. there was no noise from an engine of any kind!
i've been in aerospace work for over 60 years and never witnessed such an event.
previous ufo sighting was on dual radar pickups during a gca landing in england in 1954.
content.summary: Object traveled from s to n, aprox 800 ft. above terrain,very bright yellow/red glow, no other lights as in a/c,no noise at all

content.detailedDescription: At approx 2145 i let my dogs out in my backyard. i live in a somewhat rural area approx 10 miles northeast of weatherford, texas. there is very little light pollution and this was a cloudless night. i observed from my patio what i first thought to be aircraft landing lights over the city of weatherford due west from my location but after a few seconds i noticed they were not moving or blinking. i went inside and got my 20x80 tripod mounted binos and my 11 year old son. we took turns watching the object for approx 10 min until it set below the horizon. while observing thru the binos the object appeared to be much further away than over the city. it was clearly visible to the naked eye and similar in color to the setting sun. thru the binos the color fluctuated from white, orange, and red in no particular order. it was a near perfect circle and i can best describe it as a small much dimmer sun. i often look at the sky from my back yard at night, the viewing is typically ideal. i have observed many aircraft and satellites but have never seen anything like this before. i did not attempt to photo, as no detail could be captured.
content.summary: Glowing orange/red orb in western sky

ive still never had any experiences quite as shocking as what they describe.....Just wondering if anyone else saw this.

content.detailedDescription:
My son, marty was outside splitting wood, he yelled for me to come out to see the weird light in the sky. i went out and saw an object in the sky glowed gold all over, it looked like a cylinder with a small wing on top and on bottom, it was below and following behind a plane (we are on the dulles airport flight area)heading south west. i had my glasses on and could see the color and the shape clearly.  he noticed that there was a regular airplane in front and it has the usually red blinking light on it. when he first saw the object the plane was way ahead of it, but the object caught up, then disappeared close to the plane, he said.  i went back in to get a coat as it was really cold that night. but then he saw it disappear (blink out) and in one second it came back but then disappeared into "glitter."

size: if you hold up your hand the object was about the size of an asprin. it looked bigger than the plane. there was not sound except for the plane. i immediately jotted down the information above and made sure of what marty saw. there was not cloud cover and the sky was clear. no wind.
we can provide a sketch but do not have access to internet at home.  i am submitting this at the library.
content.summary: Object glowed gold was shaped like a plane on its side projections top and bottom followed a plane then disappeared and reappeared  turned to glitter and disappeared

content.detailedDescription:
Approximately 35 years ago, we were playing ball after dinner in front of our house. it wasn’t dark yet outside. there was no danger, except for occasional wildlife, because our farm was isolated. there was no road traffic as it was the last property on a dirt road. all the rest of our family was inside the house. after a few ball throws we have been spotted three times within split second right at us. (see drawing # 1 attached) our first thought was that a car was coming but when we looked up we saw a bright white sphere that was heading towards the field. (see drawing #2 attached) i ran towards my sister who also came to me. we were so terrified that we both grabbed the mail box post. when we noticed that the sphere was farther, we ran home to tell our family who immediately watched through the window.  one of my brothers said and i quote: “this explains the energy surge we experiment minutes ago”.  my other brother said: “it looks like the light i saw with mom when i was three”. and my mother replied: “we are not alone in the universe”. after the stress was over and the sphere gone, we wanted to return outside to continue to play. my mother told us that it was too late because it was 10h30 pm already. we were both surprise because for us, it felt like we were playing outside since a short time. 
the normal life continued, but i stayed with a feeling of strangeness… incomprehension… of missing time…
a few years later, i did a nightmare. i was on a metallic table unable to move. i felt that something was “moving” around me but i couldn’t see anything except for a device attached to the “ceiling” that was coming down towards me. i was panicked, i tried to move… they hold my head. i was told telepathically that i won’t feel any pain… i felt that my sister was near me. the device pierces my right eye with a thin needle. (see drawing #3 attached)
i calmed myself because it was true that i felt no pain. i couldn’t move, but i could move my eyes! i remembered thinking that i wasn’t cold even if i was on a metallic table. i turned my eyes to the left and i saw 2 “dark grey beings” in front of a console. there was a “tall pale grey”. when i saw him, i thought, “this one he’s different”. he then turned to the two short ones and signaled them that i was watching. so, a short one came to me. he “reassured me” that nothing bad would happen either to me or my sister… he turned my head towards a giant tv screen to my left and made me understand that if humans don’t change they will go to their destruction… by images of famines, explosions… (see drawing 4 attached)
i woke up in tears thinking to myself that this was what really happened…
content.summary: I can’t explain what my sister and i have experienced when we were teenagers. today, i’m 48 and i now dare talking about it.

content.detailedDescription:
Witness was loading pvc pipe into the back of his pick-up parked at the diesel pump at the vp gas station / convenience store on hwy 87 in sutherland springs. witness was facing southeast when he first saw the object to the southeast. it's silver reflective color caught his attention (mid day, bright sunlight). it was hovering approximately 450 feet southeast of witness's position, about 300-400 off the ground, to the right / se of hwy 87. witness had no idea what it could be so he continued to watch it. he describes the object as a silver disc about 8 - 10 feet in diameter. did not see any other markings or shapes (ie dome, lights, etc). from it's hovering position it made an "erratic" sudden move to the right (south)then ascended somewhat, tilted and began moving off toward the northeast, crossing hwy 87. witness took out is cell phone and took four photos as the object flew off toward the north. witness describes the motion of the object as it was flying off as an extended arc, similar to skeet being launched on a gun range.

witness remained in has position behind his truck throughout the sighting. he did not hear, smell or sense anything else from the object. the sighting lasted approximately 45 seconds from when it was first noticed until it flew out of sight. witness states that later in the day, he felt some anxiety, but does not think this was related to this sighting. 

please note: this initial report is being submitted by a mufon field investigator and star team member (id# 18377) whom witness has worked with in the past. witness called me to report this incident and provided the four photos he secured with his iphone. witness does not wish to remain anonymous and is open to being contacted about this event.
content.summary: Silver reflective disc, hovering when first noticed, made erratic turn to the right, ascended, then flew off in an arc pattern.

content.detailedDescription:
While i was working on a building site in adelaide australia, i was on top of some scaffolding g waiting for my labourer to bring me some more materials. i was looking at the view as it was a lovely sunny day. i noticed a very large almost transparent sphere hovering just under the cloud line, it was moving slowly around a small area. when my labourer came up to the top top of the scaffolding i pointed the sphere out and asked him if he could see it, which he could. we watched it for a further 20 mins, then in moved upwards through the clouds. the clouds dispersed as it passed through. then the sphere carried on climbing until out of sight. 
my labourer who was a local to adelaide informed me there is an air force base in that area where the sphere was hovering. the sphere seemed to be very large. 

i just want to know if anyone has seen a similar object.
content.summary: We watched a very large near transparent sphere hover above ground for at least 30mins before rising up out of site

content.detailedDescription:
My daughter and i were returning home from seattle.  we were on i 82 about 33 miles north of yakima, washington.  it was about 8:20 pm. the sky was clear, and we were enjoying the stars as they were so big and bright.  i noticed a cigar shaped object, glowing reddish-orange, hovering in the sky.  it was below the brightest star (venus?) in the sky (west of i-82) and a little to the left of it - about 60 degrees off the horizon.  i had been looking at it (off and on as i was driving) for about 2 minutes wondering what i was looking at, when my daughter (28 years old) saw it and asked what it was.  we both continued to observe it for another minute, and then it lost its glow, or else vanished. we did not observe an outline, or a dark solid shape, so we concluded it had disappeared - much to our disbelief. i have no idea at what altitude the object actually was, but i got the impression it was over a mile above the ground.  it was extremely large, but i couldn't even guess what its actual size would be. my impression is that it would be at least as large as a city block if it was on the ground.  

my daughter then told me to look at the 5 airplanes flying in the same area we had seen the object.  because we were on a curve in the highway i was only able to glance over, and did see one airplane.  i asked her if they were in formation, she reported that the airplanes were flying in a triangle pattern with two following in the rear.  we were close to a military training area, and it is possible that they had some jets in the sky - either training or looking for the object we saw.

we stopped about 29 miles north of yakima at a rest stop and scanned the sky for it, but were not able to locate it again. 

we are both wondering if anyone else saw it?
content.summary: Orange-red glowing, huge cigar shaped object hovering for 3 minutes disappeared

content.detailedDescription:
Me crié en el campo con mis abuelos y obteníamos leche y queso de las vacas de mi abuelo. para eso teníamos que apartar las crías de las vacas en la tarde para que no mamaran en la noche y poder ordeñarlas en la mañana siguiente. una de esas tardes cuando me dirigía a apartar las crías tuve un encuentro que me causo un trauma por mucho tiempo ya que lo que vi fue algo que jamas olvidare y que nunca avía visto y que hasta el día de hoy no e vuelto a ver mas que por la tv. en la tarde monte una mula para ir a separar las crías y al terminar de subir una pendiente note un zumbido al de un motor eléctrico que se escucha lejos, mi ojo inicio a buscar la dirección de donde venia el zumbido y fue en ese momento que quede en shock por unos minutos luego de eso lo que dicto y instinto lleno de temor fue huir del lugar a pedir ayuda pero en el camino de regreso pensé que nadie me creería y no conté el echo hasta barios años después.
lo que observe al buscar la fuente del zumbido fue un objeto relativamente pequeño a muy poca altura del suelo digamos unos 50 o 70 metros y yo me encontraba a unos 100 metros mas o menos del objeto así que pude observar en detalle la forma del mismo desde su color que era un color plateado como en del aluminio recién pulido reflejaba bastante la luz del sol pero se podía ver a detalle su forma tanto así que apreciara como cuando unes dos platos y en la parte de arriba tenia una cúpula trasparente como de vidrio pero no se veía a nadie dentro de ella. se veía perfectamente que el plato de arriba estaba estático pero el de abajo giraba y de en medio de los dos platos despedía un humo blanco muy blanco parecido al efecto contrail que realizan los aviones comerciales al ascender a cierta altura pero el objeto que describo estaba muy cerca del suelo así que no creo que fuera el mismo efecto. este humo salia a medida que se movía muy lento en linea recta tan lento como cuando ves desde un costado a 200 metros de una vía recta moverse un vehículo a una velocidad de unos 60 o 70 km/h. lo pude observar moverse una distancia de 100 o 200 metros por uno o dos minutos si acaso hasta que entre en pánico y salí corriendo en mi mula muy asustado así que no pude ver asia done se dirigió ni que paso después. 
después cuando regrese a encerrar a las crías aun estaba un rastro de la estela pero el objeto avia desaparecido.
en otra ocasión les grabo un vídeo del lugar exacto con coordenadas gps donde fue e echo.
aqui les dejo las coordenadas que me da el google maps -0.325951, -80.038459
content.summary: Objeto a plena luz del día a una distancia legible

content.detailedDescription: My daughter and i were driving at night in the dark when we noticed 4 lights that looked very bright above the distant mountains. four of them lined up next to one another from right to left. they stayed stationary for a few moments and then 1 would fly swiftly away from the others leaving 3 in a linear horizontal line before it disappeared. it would spontaneously reappear and then fly above the other 3, move left again and then realign with the other 4 leaving 4 brightly shining in the sky. we also saw a distant airplane but it appeared farther away, higher and with blinking lights. the ufos we saw were solid bright white/yellow and were brilliant against the night sky. they flew fluidly, and would move great lengths across the sky in an instant, disappearing and reappearing. they were much larger than stars in the sky and brighter than the brightest star. we felt excited and in awe, and happy they would reappear so we could get good pictures and videos. our neighbors also saw them while out driving. we finally left to go home. we have seen them before in a dark night sky over the estrella mountains to the east. they are common in this part of goodyear. we see them several times a year.
content.summary: 4 lights in sky over mountains, blinked, lined up in a linear fashion from right to left, 1- 2 would rove up and to the side before disappearing and the spontaneously reappearing

content.detailedDescription: I first witnessed the light last week before yesterday's recoding (jan21) i noticed it because my dog was glued to the window looking up at  it and he never does that so i looked and saw it. i normally would of over looked it thinking it was a star but something drew me to it. i became curious and starting looking outside at it. when i went outside to look at it closer. i noticed my dog didn't want to go outside. still watching it and since i've had a hard time getting my dog to go outside. i noticed this again yesterday and the only reason why i noticed it is cause since last week i'm always checking now. it doesn't move, it just hovers. the first night i watched it disappear without even flying away it just vanished. so this time i wanted to try and capture that and i got my phone out to record it. i decided to try and zoom in and when i zoomed to the max i noticed that it looked like the ufo you see on tv and it terrified me. i had a really hard time sleeping mainly due to me not being able to understand this. i did not witness it disappearing this time as i walked away to do something came back and it was gone. i've noticed that both times i've seen it, it has hovered for a hour or a little more before it disappears. also the light is far away but not as high up as a star. each pic i zoomed in more. it never moved closer to me
content.summary: This looks like a really bright star, but it looks nothing like the other stars and is no where near as high as other stars
